premise_source_doc_sentence: In the United States and Canada it has sold less than 10,000 copies as of September 2011 .
Although House of Love sold less than half of what its predecessor sold , it similarly combines pop music with Christian values .
The album has been certified five times platinum by the RIAA in the United States , has sold 10 million copies worldwide and remains Soundgarden 's most successful album .

The album went on to sell 120,000 copies in France , 80,000 copies in the Netherlands , 50,000 copies in Mexico , 35,000 copies in Belgium , 30,000 copies in Poland , 20,000 copies in Romania , 20,000 copies in Portugal , 15,000 copies in Hungary and approximately 20,000 copies in the United Kingdom .
Copies of this album sold in Europe , Australia , and Japan feature the additional track `` Politics of Kissing '' .
